channel.title: [614] - RuneDesign Release
channel.description:
[color=black]I just dont feel like coding 614s anymore. Seriously, that's all I can. Ive been working really hard on this, and im proud to release. This has no anti leechs, no MySQL, nothing. I do not want this to be released on anywhere else then google! Im gonna start again with a 317 server, and learn java coding after school. I wish everyone good luck with this, and I hope you enjoy this. Please use the thanks button, and leave a comment. Feel free to rep or anything else. If I see this anywhere else then R-S, then I will delete all links, and flame ya 24/7. I only want to have it uploaded on my dropbox. If i see another mirror, I will close this thread.
My server was online about 1 month, and my max player amount was only 20..
More info can be found Here
If you need any help, or if you have errors etc please feel free to report them. I don't care about leechers. Feel free to leech anything you want, but please give some Credits and show some respect.
Some features: - Workign Teleblock with timer - Working Trading without item duplication - Working Dicing - Working Potion system/eating system - Perfect combat (No overpowered items) - 100% Antiflood - 50% Working friendlist - NO NULLPOINTERS! Stable source - Working bonuses - Super Donator/Premium Donator/Legit Dicer - Working leeches - No dupes - 6 Different PK spots - 3 Multi zones - Usefull commands - Blood/Miasmic barrage - Working Ring of Vigour - Working divine affects[/color]
